stories.text: Hello HN! My name is Haruna Oseni currently an International student at Houston Community College, also working as a freelance Software Engineer and part time programming tutor @HCC (Javascript , python etc.), I am more of a generalist engineer (front end, now playing around with backend, done some data science and more), I enjoy being uncomfortable and tackling hard projects which I have no idea how to even begin then learning what I need to get the job done, I am currently working on an app (startup), watch, the goal is to basically enable users experience more during a video call. I will be graduating from HCC may 18. Writing software is an obsession at this point, I'm very interested in consumer product, fintech(payment), logistics software etc. After graduation to be honest guys, I want to find like minded individuals/team whose dream is to build an insanely successful company, or looking for a cofounder or a team member, hell, just little help on their startup. If that resonates with you, shoot me an email (harunaoseni23@gmail.com), lets change the world (seriously, I will literally relocate after graduation without seconds thoughts if anyone here resonates with this, note: I could care less about a salary atm)!! sorry for the long text guys.... here's my hub of git, cheers --> https://github.com/harunaOseni
